torch

Usage:
Runs deep learning models for summarization and translation (BART & MarianMT).

Install:

pip install torch

transformers

Usage:
Loads and manages NLP transformer models for text summarization and translation.

Install:

pip install transformers

sentencepiece

Usage:
Provides subword tokenization required for MarianMT translation models.

Install:

pip install sentencepiece

SpeechRecognition

Usage:
Converts speech to text using online APIs (Google Speech Recognition).

Install:

pip install SpeechRecognition

vosk

Usage:
Enables offline speech recognition without internet connectivity.

Install: "pip install vosk"

pyaudio

Usage:
Captures microphone audio for both online and offline speech recognition.

Install: "pip install pyaudio"


⚠️ If installation fails:

Windows: install prebuilt wheel

Linux: sudo apt install portaudio19-dev

macOS: brew install portaudio

ping3

Usage:
Checks internet connectivity to switch between online and offline modes.

Install: "pip install ping3"
